race.description: Greyhounds As Pets Grade 5 Series F Pr1 Division1
race.comment: IRINKA BENJI (1) was an outstanding 22.73 winner at this track last start. Expected to go close again if runs up to latest time. HI THERE FRANK (8) was a hot course and distance winner last time, claiming a Grade 5 in a blistering 22.72 and a new PB here. Smart winner latest and looks a key chance on that form. GOLD BENZ (7) recorded one of the quickest times on the card this course and distance last time, finishing second in a Grade 5 in 22.68 and a new PB here. Should be in this for a long way. SAILAWAY BUDDY (2) is always a threat when he races at this journey.
